             JOYCE. I am shopman to a pawnbroker. I have a suit of clothes, pawned by Valentine.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300415-151-person1358">
                  WILLIAM 
                  GEORGE
               <interp inst="t18300415-151-person1358" type="surname" value="GEORGE"></interp>
